    <p>We believe that blending a systematic research processes with fundamental analyst research leads to superior results.</p>
    <p>By combining an unbiased, systematic investment process with fundamental analysis, the Toreador Reseach and Trading (TRT) seeks to minimize the impact of these and other wealth destroying factors on the stocks we own, while uncovering superior investment ideas across economic sectors to achieve Toreador Research and Trading’s goal of providing superior long term returns to our investors.</p></div>
